        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "\"Upon my word, Sir Philip, you are right-that wine is the best I have-you certainly have a most discriminating taste,\" said the complaisant wine merchant.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
