        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "\"I'll tell you what,\" cried Sir Philip, \"the thing is this: by Jove! now, there's no possibility now-no possibility now, by Jove! of imposing upon me.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
