        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5980/22680/5980_22680_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "\"Dine with me, Clarence,\" said Rochfort, \"and we'll crown you with three times three; and,\" whispered he to Sir Philip, \"we'll have another trial after dinner.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5980_22680_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5980/22680/5980_22680_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "Clarence not being used to drink in a morning, though all his companions were, was much affected by the wine, and Rochfort proposed that they should take a turn in the park to cool Hervey's head.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
