        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5980/22680/5980_22680_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "They were exactly even for some yards, then Clarence got ahead of Sir Philip, and he reached the elm tree first; but as he waved his hat, exclaiming, \"Clarence has won the day,\" Sir Philip came up with his companions, and coolly informed him that he had lost his wager-\"Lost! lost!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
