        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5980/22680/5980_22680_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "\"I'm off, by Jove!\" said Sir Philip.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5980_22680_000019_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5980/22680/5980_22680_000019_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "\"I'm too hot, damme, to walk with you any more-but I'm your man if you've a mind for a swim-here's the Serpentine river, Clarence-hey? damn it!--hey?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5980_22680_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5980/22680/5980_22680_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "Sir Philip and all his companions knew that Clarence had never learned to swim.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5980_22680_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5980/22680/5980_22680_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "\"You may wink at one another, as wisely as you please,\" said Clarence, \"but come on, my boys-I am your man for a swim-hundred guineas upon it!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5980_22680_000023_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5980/22680/5980_22680_000023_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "Rochfort, and all the other young men stood laughing by the river side.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5980_22680_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5980/22680/5980_22680_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "\"Who the devil are these two that seem to be making up to us?\" said Sir Philip, looking at two gentlemen who were coming towards them; \"saint George, hey?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5980_22680_000024_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5980/22680/5980_22680_000024_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "you know every body.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5980_22680_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5980/22680/5980_22680_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "\"The foremost is Percival, of Oakly park, I think, 'pon my honour,\" replied mr saint George, and he then began to settle how many thousands a year mr Percival was worth.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5980_22680_000025_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5980/22680/5980_22680_000025_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "This point was not decided when the gentlemen came up to the spot where Sir Philip was standing.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5980_22680_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5980/22680/5980_22680_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "The child for whose sake Clarence Hervey had lost his bet was mr Percival's, and he came to thank him for his civility.--The gentleman who accompanied mr Percival was an old friend of Clarence Hervey's; he had met him abroad, but had not seen him for some years.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5980_22680_000027_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5980/22680/5980_22680_000027_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "I think I saw him pass by me just now.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5980_22680_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5980/22680/5980_22680_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "\"Damn it, yes-where is Clary, though?\" exclaimed Sir Philip, suddenly recollecting himself.--Clarence Hervey at this instant was drowning: he had got out of his depth, and had struggled in vain to recover himself.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5980_22680_000029_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5980/22680/5980_22680_000029_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "\"Curse me, if it's not all over with Clary,\" continued Sir Philip.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5980_22680_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5980/22680/5980_22680_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "\"Damme, so it is,\" said Rochfort; \"but he's so heavy in his clothes, he'd pull me down along with him to Davy's locker:--damme, if I'll go after him.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5980_22680_000032_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5980/22680/5980_22680_000032_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "Clarence Hervey was absolutely senseless.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
