        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "\"No danger of that,\" said Rochfort; \"for how can one meet with oneself in a book, Sir Philip, if one never opens one?--By Jove, that's the true way.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
