        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "\"But, 'pon my honour,\" said saint George, \"I should like of all things to see myself in print; 'twould make one famously famous.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
