        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "\"Damn me, if I don't flatter myself, though, one can make oneself famous enough to all intents and purposes without having any thing to say to these author geniuses.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
