        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "You're a famous fellow, faith! to want to see yourself in print-I'll publish this in Bond street: damn it, in point of famousness, I'd sport my Random against all the books that ever were read or written, damn me!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
