        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "When Clarence Hervey came to his senses he started up, rubbed his eyes, and looked about, exclaiming-\"What's all this?--Where am I?--Where's Baddely?--Where's Rochfort?--Where are they all?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
