        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "\"Gone home to dinner,\" answered mr saint George, who was a hanger on of Sir Philip's; \"but they left me to bring you after them.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
