    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5980_22680_000052_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5980/22680/5980_22680_000052_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "This, sir, is no less a man than mr Clarence Hervey, of whose universal genius you have just had a specimen; for which he was crowned with sedges, as he well deserved, by the god of the Serpentine river.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5980_22680_000052_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5980/22680/5980_22680_000052_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "Do not be so unjust as to imagine that he has any of the presumption which is sometimes the chief characteristic of a man of universal genius.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5980_22680_000052_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5980/22680/5980_22680_000052_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "mr Clarence Hervey is, without exception, the most humble man of my acquaintance; for whilst all good judges would think him fit company for mr Percival, he has the humility to think himself upon a level with mr Rochfort and Sir Philip Baddely.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5980_22680_000053_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5980/22680/5980_22680_000053_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "\"You have lost as little of your satirical wit, dr X----, as of your active benevolence, I perceive,\" said Clarence Hervey, \"since I met you abroad.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5980_22680_000053_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5980/22680/5980_22680_000053_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "But as I cannot submit to your unjust charge of humility, will you tell me where you are to be found in town, and to morrow------\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5980_22680_000054_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5980/22680/5980_22680_000054_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "\"To morrow, and to morrow, and to morrow,\" said dr X----: \"why not to day?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5980_22680_000055_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5980/22680/5980_22680_000055_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "\"I am engaged,\" said Clarence, hesitating and laughing---\"I am unfortunately engaged to day to dine with mr Rochfort and Sir Philip Baddely, and in the evening I am to be at Lady Delacour's.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5980_22680_000056_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5980/22680/5980_22680_000056_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "\"Lady Delacour!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5980_22680_000056_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5980/22680/5980_22680_000056_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "Not the same Lady Delacour whom four years ago, when we met at Florence, you compared to the Venus de Medici-no, no, it cannot be the same-a goddess of four years' standing!--Incredible!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5980_22680_000057_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5980/22680/5980_22680_000057_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "\"Incredible as it seems,\" said Clarence, \"it is true: I admire her ladyship more than ever I did.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
