        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5980/22680/5980_22680_000058_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "\"Like a true connoisseur,\" said dr X----, \"you admire a fine picture the older it grows: I hear that her ladyship's face is really one of the finest pieces of painting extant, with the advantage of",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5980_22680_000060_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5980/22680/5980_22680_000060_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "\"Come, come, dr X----,\" cried mr Percival, \"no more wit at Lady Delacour's expense: I have a fellow feeling for mr Hervey.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
