        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "\"To morrow you shall know the how, the when, and the where,\" said mr Percival: \"here's your friend, mr saint George, and his coach.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
