        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5980",
        "content": "\"I can't say particularly, upon my soul,\" replied mr saint George; \"for my own part, I was in boots, so you know I was out of the question.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
